    {
      "Text": "This update for tiff fixes the following issues:\n\nUpdate to 4.7.1:\n\n- CVE-2025-8851: Fixed stack-based buffer overflow (bsc#1248278).\n- CVE-2025-9900: Fixed write-what-where via TIFFReadRGBAImageOriented (bsc#1250413).\n",
